# Narrative Engine Diagram

## ROGUE NEURAL - Narrative Generation Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant LLM as Groq LLM
    participant Prompt as Prompt Builder
    participant Context as Context Manager
    participant Cache as Response Cache
    participant Handler as Narrative Handler

    actor User

    Loop Each Phase
        User->>Handler: Request Phase Content
        Handler->>Context: Get Current Context
        Context->>Context: Scenario + Chaos Level + History
        Context-->>Handler: Context Object

        Handler->>Prompt: Build System Prompt
        Prompt->>Prompt: Load Persona Template
        Prompt->>Prompt: Add Scenario Context
        Prompt->>Prompt: Set Tone (Chaos-Dependent)
        Prompt-->>Handler: System Prompt

        Handler->>Prompt: Build User Prompt
        Prompt->>Prompt: Current Phase Requirements
        Prompt->>Prompt: Choice Constraints
        Prompt-->>Handler: User Prompt

        Handler->>Cache: Check Cache
        Cache-->>Handler: Cache Hit? / Miss

        alt Cache Miss
            Handler->>LLM: Request Generation
            LLM->>LLM: Process Context
            LLM-->>Handler: Raw Response

            Handler->>Cache: Store in Cache
            Handler->>Handler: Parse Response
            Handler->>Handler: Validate Schema
        else Cache Hit
            Handler->>Handler: Load from Cache
        end

        Handler->>Context: Update History
        Handler-->>User: Formatted Narrative
    end
```

