## ROGUE NEURAL - Context Management

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class ContextManager {
        -scenario: Scenario
        -chaosLevel: number
        -phaseHistory: PhaseResult[]
        -entityStates: Map~Entity, State~
        +getContext()
        +updateChaos(delta: number)
        +addPhaseResult(result: PhaseResult)
        +getEntityState(entity: Entity)
        +updateEntityState(entity: Entity, newState: State)
    }

    class Scenario {
        +id: string
        +title: string
        +description: string
        +initialChaos: number
    }

    class PhaseResult {
        +phaseId: string
        +choiceId: string
        +chaosChange: number
        +narrativeChanges: NarrativeChange[]
    }

    class NarrativeChange {
        +type: ChangeType
        +target: string
        +value: string | number
    }

    class EntityState {
        +entityId: string
        +trust: number
        +fear: number
        +knowledge: number
        +lastInteraction: Date
    }

    ContextManager "1" --> "1" Scenario : manages
    ContextManager "1" --> "0..*" PhaseResult : tracks
    ContextManager "1" --> "0..*" EntityState : tracks
```

