## ROGUE NEURAL - Internal Monologue System

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle: Entity Spawn

    Idle: Waiting for Interaction
    Idle --> Analyzing: User Spoken

    Analyzing: Assess Context
    Analyzing --> Planning: Context Understood

    Planning: Determine Response
    Planning --> Monologuing: Decision Made

    Monologuing: Internal Thought
    Monologuing --> Waiting: Thought Complete

    Waiting: Before Next Interaction
    Waiting --> Analyzing: User Spoken Again

    Note right of Idle
        Entity calculates chaos impact
        and potential outcomes
    end note

    Note right of Analyzing
        Analyzes tone, context,
        and entity relationships
    end note

    Note right of Planning
        Chooses response strategy
        balancing chaos and survival
    end note

    Note right of Monologuing
        Generates internal thought
        with entity personality
    end note
```

